cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "SomaliWeb v1 — A Quality-Filtered Somali Web Corpus with a Matched Tokenizer"
message: >-
  If you use this corpus, the tokenizer, or the construction pipeline,
  please cite the corresponding work using the metadata below.
